## 6. Real-Time Socket.io Event Map

All three surfaces join a booking room: `room:booking_{bookingId}`

| Event | Emitter | Listeners | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| `new_booking` | Client App | Admin, Driver | Patient submits booking form |
| `booking_accepted` | Admin | Client, Driver | Admin accepts booking |
| `ambulance_dispatched` | Admin | Client, Driver | Admin dispatches ambulance |
| `driver_accepted` | Driver App | Admin, Client | Driver accepts the trip |
| `driver_denied` | Driver App | Admin | Driver denies — admin reassigns |
| `driver_location_update` | Driver App | Client, Admin | GPS every 5 seconds |
| `patient_location_update` | Client App | Driver, Admin | GPS every 5 seconds |
| `trip_completed` | Driver App | Client, Admin | Trip ended — show rating page |
| `payment_confirmed` | Admin | Client | Payment confirmed |

