## 7. Full Backend API

### Auth
```
POST /auth/login/admin         — email + password → returns JWT + role
POST /auth/login/driver        — driver_name + driver_id → returns JWT + role
POST /auth/register            — company/admin registration
POST /auth/refresh             — refresh access token
POST /auth/logout
POST /auth/forgot-password
POST /auth/reset-password
```

### Companies
```
GET  /companies                — list all companies (public — for client map)
GET  /companies/:id
```

### Ambulances & Drivers
```
GET  /ambulances               — list with filters
POST /ambulances               — register new ambulance (admin only)
PATCH /ambulances/:id/status   — activate / deactivate
GET  /location/ambulances/nearby  — public, returns available units by proximity
POST /drivers                  — register new driver (admin only)
GET  /drivers
GET  /drivers/:id
PATCH /drivers/:id
```

### Bookings
```
GET  /bookings                 — list (admin, filtered by company)
POST /bookings                 — create (public — client app)
GET  /bookings/:id
PATCH /bookings/:id/assign     — admin assigns ambulance + driver
PATCH /bookings/:id/accept     — admin accepts
PATCH /bookings/:id/dispatch   — admin dispatches
PATCH /bookings/:id/arrive     — driver marks arrived
PATCH /bookings/:id/complete   — driver completes trip
PATCH /bookings/:id/cancel     — driver or admin cancels
PATCH /bookings/:id/deny       — driver denies request
```

### Location
```
POST /location/patient         — client updates patient GPS
POST /location/driver          — driver updates GPS
```

### Payments
```
GET  /payments                 — admin views all
PATCH /payments/:id/confirm    — admin confirms
```

### Feedback
```
POST /feedback                 — client submits rating
GET  /feedback                 — admin views all
```

### Reports
```
GET  /reports/:type?startDate=&endDate=&ambulanceId=&driverId=&status=&paymentStatus=
```

