## 10. Key Design Rules

1. **One login page, smart routing** — role detected server-side, redirect client-side
2. **Admins use email + password** — drivers use name + driver ID
3. **Drivers created by admin only** — no self-serve driver registration
4. **Each company's units show separately on client** — patients see and choose by company
5. **Dispatch always shows real names** — Company Name + Driver Name + Driver ID + call buttons
6. **Admin sees driver responses in real-time** — accepted, denied, or timed out
7. **Driver app is SafeBoda-style** — full-screen incoming request, accept/deny with timeout
8. **Everything syncs** — all booking state changes propagate instantly to all three surfaces via Socket.io rooms
9. **Single database** — client app, admin, and driver app all read/write the same tables
10. **Maps everywhere use Leaflet + OpenStreetMap** — no Google Maps, no API key required